---

<section class="section-pad" id="approach">
  <div class="wrap manifesto">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>The idea</p>
    <h2 class="display m-title" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="0.05">
      Named for a bush — <br />
      <span class="grad-text">built to keep growing.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="m-grid">
      <p class="m-lead" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="0.1">
        A bush doesn't finish. It branches, adapts, reaches for light, and thickens
        season after season. That is how we think about a trading firm: not a fixed
        formula, but a living system that compounds — capital, code, and conviction
        growing together.
      </p>
      <p class="m-body" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="0.15">
        Markets never stand still, so neither do we. Every model is a hypothesis under
        constant revision; every edge decays and must be re-earned. We stay in step with
        the market's own tempo — researching, measuring, and rebuilding on a path with a
        single direction: <span class="gold">on the way to perfection.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="m-marquee" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="m-track">
        <span>Research</span><span>·</span><span>Measure</span><span>·</span>
        <span>Deploy</span><span>·</span><span>Adapt</span><span>·</span>
        <span>Compound</span><span>·</span>
        <span>Research</span><span>·</span><span>Measure</span><span>·</span>
        <span>Deploy</span><span>·</span><span>Adapt</span><span>·</span>
        <span>Compound</span><span>·</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .m-title { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 4.4rem); margin: 1rem 0 3rem; }
  .m-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .m-lead { font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.2vw, 1.7rem); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.45; }
  .m-body { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted); }

  .m-marquee {
    margin-top: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--panel-brd);
    padding-block: 1.4rem;
    overflow: hidden; mask-image: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #000 12%, #000 88%, transparent);
  }
  .m-track {
    display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--muted-2);
    animation: scrollx 26s linear infinite;
  }
  .m-track span:nth-child(3n+1) { color: var(--violet-300); }
  @keyframes scrollx { to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .m-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
